event.title: FOSS City Meetup Kanpur
event.metaDesc: Join the FOSS United community in Kanpur for their second meetup focused on open source software.
event.content: Join the FOSS United community in Kanpur for their second meetup focused on open source software. This in-person gathering provides an opportunity to connect with fellow open source enthusiasts, developers, and maintainers in the Kanpur area.
